# Visual Studio / MSBuild output for every project under host/ — bin, obj, Debug/Release
# artifacts, staticwebassets caches, scopedcss, dswa caches, the .vs solution folder, etc.
# Blanket rule; do not replace with individually-listed generated files (they drift every
# build). If `git status` still shows a bin/ or obj/ file as modified, it was committed
# before this rule existed — `git rm --cached <path>` to untrack it (this rule then applies).
host/**/bin/**
host/**/obj/**
host/**/.vs/
*.slnx.user

